        <ownedComment xmi:id="_17_0_3beta_f980370_1347884164490_467706_2855" body="AMU exists in the resource A (module of the project) pointing to resource B (another module, main project) but there is no direct or indirect path of normal/user-defined module usages from resource A to resource B. But there is a direct or indirect path of normal/user-defined module usages from main project to resource B." annotatedElement="_17_0_3beta_f980370_1347883858878_631667_2712">
